== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
'''Mukakigeli Mireille''' ni  umutaramyi mu birori bitandukanye yaba mu bukwe, akaba n'umukobwa udasazwe mu gusohora abageni mu bukwe. N'umuririmbyi muri Gakondo uhimba ibihangano ndetse unafite alubumu y'indirimbo za gakondo. Mukakigeli  yakuze kunda umuziki umeze nk'ikintu gitembera mu maraso kuko na se umubyara yari intore. Mukakigeli yitabiriye Tusker Project Fame ariko ntiyabasha gukomeza, atangira kuririmba yakora umuziki wa Jazz&Blues ariko aza guhindura akajya aririmba gakondo . Ajya atumirwa hanze aho akubutse mu [[suwede]] aho yari yatumiwe na ambasade yu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] muri [[suwede]]. <ref>https://igihe.com/umuco/article/imvano-y-ubuhanzi-bwa-mireille-mukakigeli-wihebeye-umuziki-gakondo</ref>

